<quantity box="[331,440,1793,1819]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.03" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" unit="mm" value="30.3">30.3 mm</quantity>
SL. Dorsal profile slightly convex from snout to end of dorsal­fin base, approximately straight on caudal peduncle. Ventral profile convex on head, almost straight from anterior portion of venter to end of anal­fin base, nearly straight to slightly concave on caudal peduncle. Body slender, subcylindrical anteriorly, slightly deeper than wide, to compressed posteriorly. Greatest body depth at level of pelvic­fin base.
</paragraph>
